(1918, 'frFR', 'You find a nasty ball of water and decide to bring it to me? &nbsp;Who am I, the Earthen Ring or something?$B$BActually, that does give me an idea... perhaps you do need the Earthen Ring for this. &nbsp;I mean, if it helps clear up the situation at the lake for good, then I\'m all for it.$B$BYou know who the Earthen Ring are, &lt;name&gt;?', 18019),
