(1938, 'frFR', 'I feared that Morganth had hidden the book elsewhere, or that he had found a way to open it and read its contents.$B$BIt is good to see that he did not, and that the seals we placed on Ur\'s Treatise on Shadow Magic still hold.', 18019),
