(8907, 'frFR', 'Excellent! &nbsp;Let\'s perform the trade then. &nbsp;It\'s hard to part with this excellent armor, but I\'m afraid I won\'t be needing it any time soon.$B$BIf you\'re interested in performing more work for me, I might be willing to give up the rest of the pieces.', 18019),
