(8918, 'frFR', 'Ah, yes. &nbsp;That old goblin shall be quite happy with this blood.$B$BThose bracers were part of a larger armor set. &nbsp;If you\'re interested in providing me with further assistance I\'d be willing to consider parting with the rest of it.', 18019),
