(8921, 'frFR', 'These are precisely the materials I needed. &nbsp;Quite timely too, &lt;name&gt;!$B$BIn mere moments I will have your distiller ready to go! &nbsp;In the meantime, take this as a reward for aiding me in my project.', 18019),
(8922, 'frFR', 'Excellent! &nbsp;Just as I was running low!$B$BYou say Deliana sent you?', 18019),
