(8945, 'frFR', 'Thank you for rescuing me... I feared for my life. &nbsp;Please accept this as a small token of my gratitude.$B$BAnthion is... no... he can\'t be...', 18019),
(8946, 'frFR', '', 18019),
(8947, 'frFR', 'Excellent. &nbsp;I shall transmute these into something more suitable to our needs.', 18019),
